<subSubSection lastPageId="3" lastPageNumber="145" pageId="2" pageNumber="144" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,1675,2014]" pageId="2" pageNumber="144">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,312,1954,1978]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="144" reason="1">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Reddish yellow with black/brown markings on mesoscutum and posterior tergite; occipital carina entirely absent; mesosternum with posterior transverse carina complete but weak medially; fore wing vein 
<emphasis box="[1176,1236,1990,2014]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="144">1cu-a</emphasis>
opposite 
<emphasis box="[1337,1408,1991,2014]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="144">M&amp;RS</emphasis>
.
</paragraph>
