.
</taxonomicNameLabel>
(AI = cd/ab, CI = gf/fh, DI = k/fe, ICI = ab/cb, SDI = fe/ig, SI =
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1436,1902,2023]" box="[151,1318,1999,2023]" pageId="3" pageNumber="145">
l/j, SRI =ce/fe); D. Central part of hind wing of 
<taxonomicName authority="Pham &amp; Matsumoto &amp; Cao &amp; Shimizu, 2022" authorityName="Pham &amp; Matsumoto &amp; Cao &amp; Shimizu" authorityYear="2022" box="[637,768,1999,2023]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Stauropoctonus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="145" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="inaequalis" status="sp. nov.">
