Shimizu &amp; Lima
</taxonomicName>
, female from Vietnam: A. head, frontal view; B. head, dorsal view; C. head, lateral view; D. mesosoma, lateral view; E. mesoscutum; F. scutellum and propodeum, dorsal view; scale bar = 1mm
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption pageId="5" pageNumber="147" startId="5.[151,250,1951,1975]" targetBox="[154,1433,181,1928]" targetPageId="5">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,1951,2042]" box="[151,1437,1951,1976]" pageId="5" pageNumber="147">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,275,1951,1975]" pageId="5" pageNumber="147">FIGURE 4.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="Pham &amp; Matsumoto &amp; Cao &amp; Shimizu, 2022" authorityName="Pham &amp; Matsumoto &amp; Cao &amp; Shimizu" authorityYear="2022" box="[282,552,1952,1976]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Stauropoctonus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="147" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="inaequalis" status="sp. nov.">
